, 
<figureCitation box="[869,920,1915,1941]" captionStart="FIGURE 92" captionStartId="194.[151,250,1169,1193]" captionTargetBox="[151,1437,181,1145]" captionTargetId="figure-19@194.[151,1437,181,1145]" captionTargetPageId="194" captionText="FIGURE 92. Environment of Zhangmu Valley (樟木沟). Environment of Youyiqiao (友谊桥) (A, B), Lixin Village (ĒẾ村) (C) and Qu Township (DZ乡) (D). Photo Credit: A, B by Jian-Qing Zhu; C, D by Wen-Xuan Bi." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6340957" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6340957/files/figure.png" pageId="64" pageNumber="65">92C</figureCitation>
